channel.title: FreedomX 718/742 - Full Release
channel.description:
Hey everyone,
If anyone remembers me, I'm the maker of Panic PvP.
Why am I releasing something that I've sold before? People that bought the source gave it away and it leaked out.
The source is uploaded on Uppit so it'll last a while. The client on the other hand is uploaded on Dropbox, so if anyone mirrors it, thank you. FreedomX belongs to the community now.
[QUOTE=BongoProd;4090709][CENTER][IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/4qo7kj.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/29ay0iq.png[/img]
We are back with FreedomX! Since we went down, I’ve been making nonstop updates and bug fixes. Me and my old friends have decided to downgrade back to the 742 cache as this cache brought us the best time of our lives. [B] Features:[/B]
- 11 Custom bosses - 25/25 Skills working - Prestige system up to 10 prestiges - Hans gives veteran capes based on your online time - 2 Quests - All the Matrix minigames and 3 others made by me - Use the sawmill to make planks and use these to create the nicest furniture - Dungeoneering where you can choose what you want to kill (Har'lakk the Riftsplitter or his minions) - Loyalty Points & Pk Points - The Abyss 100% like RS - Full Living Rock Caverns - Clue Scrolls - Over 20 NPC caves - Penguin Hide and Seek - 100% Bird’s Nests like RS
And much more to discover in the world of FreedomX
Player made commentary: (very old, that spot doesn't exist anymore) [url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DIRd4eq5e0A]Watch this video to find out whats in it (copyright problems lul) - YouTube[/url]

If you read it all the way to here then I've got something for you.
You have to replace the Interfacemanager.java with this one in order to make it work correctly: [url=https://www.dropbox.com/s/1spkud7dd4rn827/InterfaceManager.java]https://www.dropbox.com/s/1spkud7dd4rn827/InterfaceManager.java[/url]

Jake
